ú|*]]), '''Turcua''' (Latin), '''Tureuku''' / '''T'urŭk'u''' - {{lang|ko|투르쿠}} (Korean), '''Turu''' (Estonian),{{listref|KNAB}} '''Turku''' (Azeri, Finnish, Latvian, Romanian, Sami[[:se:Turku|*]], Turkish), '''Turku''' - {{lang|ru|Турку}} (Russian[[:ru:Турку|*]]){{listref|KNAB}} |- | [[Tver]] | '''Kalinin''' (former name), '''Tver''' (Azeri, Italian, Romanian, Slovene, Swedish), '''Twer''' (Polish, German), '''Tvera''' (Latvian), '''Tverė''' (Lithuanian), '''Ćvier''' - {{lang|be|Цвер}} ({{lang|be|Цьвер}}) (Belarusian), '''Tiveri''' (Karelian), '''Tver''' - {{lang|uk|Твер}} (Ukrainian) |- | [[Tyszowce]] | '''Tishevits''' - {{lang|yi|טישעװיץ}} (Yiddish), '''Tyszowce''' (Polish) |}
